item.title: CVE-2022-34404|2024-08-03T09:07:16.153Z -- dell -- system%20update
item.description: Dell System Update, version 2.0.0 and earlier, contains an Improper Certificate Validation in data parser module. A local attacker with high privileges could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to credential theft and/or denial of service.
